parameters: 3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Mercenary Leon: I was blindfolded and brought here, but
where exactly is this?
Queen Caron: Oh... This is quite an impressive mercenary.
Queen Caron: Hehe, you may remove the blindfold now.
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
Mercenary Leon: C-Can you really grant my wish?

Queen Caron: There is no wish that I cannot grant, go ahead
and tell me.

Mercenary Leon: Could I be officially enlisted in General
Atu's unit?

Mercenary Leon: I have trained to demonstrate my strength to
the world. I want to become an official soldier and achieve
military success under the command of the general!
Queen Caron: Alright, I understand. I will grant your wish.
Mercenary Leon: T-Thank you very much!

Queen Caron: I will inform my subordinates of the details,
you may leave.

Mercenary Leon: Understood! I will definitely achieve
military success and repay Queen Caron and the empire!
Imperial Shadow Soldier: Hah! How may I assist you?
Queen Caron: Hmph, there is no need to ask me.
Imperial Shadow Soldier: Understood, as usual...

Queen Caron: Hehe, this pleasure of devouring ephemeral
dreams... It's more delightful than any luxury
confectionery. I can't wait for the next prey.
